{"tid":1991832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係講笑 賓施馬係被嚴重低估嘅前鋒","createTime":"2020-04-27T17:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T06:18:21.000Z","uid":199081,"like":11,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"45a5c4f7024c484c649bf93633c8ab1f3dc3d658","tid":1991832,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"喺里昂已經好撚勁 一人之力摧毀曼聯<br />\n去到皇馬做副手都好掂 有個打緊前鋒嘅進攻中場<br />\n墮後拎波做假九 搶點hold波嘅柱躉中鋒 拉邊單打嘅翼鋒 派牌嘅進攻中場 入返禁區做埋門嘅正常前鋒 呢啲佢全部都做到<br />\n個人盤扭技術同傳波都好頂級 喺邊路扭又得傳又得 根本mark唔到<br />\n多功能之餘仲要易夾 由牙朗 巴爾 摩迪變到而家雲尼素斯 華維迪 伊斯高都夾到<br />\n十幾歲踢到三十頭仲大把貨交<br />\n而家已經係唔少歐聯同西甲入波紀錄嘅頭幾<br />\n仲要又靚仔又識拍片又識揸快車<br />\n可惜國家隊俾電甘視針對 如果唔係應該拎埋歐國盃 世界盃 歐國聯<br />\n但無阻佢全盛時期起碼世五呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n球王片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pTARzcWmODk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpTARzcWmODk&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=92d270e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pTARzcWmODk</a>"},{"pid":"8b888ff3eed4082b5549c108a29cd70d1a3b4089","tid":1991832,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"話佢廢嘅人根本唔識足球"},{"pid":"8ea057bd66ffc9bbb9e35fddb11199b5bad98b81","tid":1991832,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daa22eea0baea8bdb5463dd4ddb0c54b783f4e4","tid":1991832,"uid":27321,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:11:52.000Z","msg":"犯罪都勁 真係全能"},{"pid":"14c9a6112368ca43d8c172986deda7b13bdaf006","tid":1991832,"uid":371,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:23:06.000Z","msg":"仲識勒索，真正全能到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a56d7a6d7f441c2707369045de9f76b544fffc3","tid":1991832,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:29:02.000Z","msg":"世五<img src=\"/ass